channel.title: Comments on: Old video gold, Babes in Toyland, and Courtney Love has always sucked

item.title: By: Arthur
item.dc:creator: Arthur
item.description: Good on MTV, but I'll be happier when it passes my Thrashing Doves and Kitchens of Distinction database test. (Both were played on 120M, but like you said, there is probably more to come.)
